data.description: Tucked away in the Belair addition, this 4 bedroom home offers a versatile second living or dining room & generous laundry room perfect for an office or hobby space. Revel in updates like a 2021 roof, chic living room flooring, and revamped guest shower with lifetime warranty. Vinyl double pane windows. The covered patio's a sweet spot for relaxation. Decked attic provides storage galore! Just steps away from neighborhood park w/tennis, basketball & jungle gym. Possible VA Assumption. Home Warranty Included
